			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Technical measures for irrigation to replenish the water needed by crops. In order to ensure the normal growth of crops and obtain high and stable yield, crops must be supplied with sufficient water. Under natural conditions, it is often unable to meet the water requirements of crops because of insufficient precipitation or uneven distribution. Therefore, irrigation must be carried out artificially to make up for the lack of natural rainfall.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">灌溉为地补充作物所需水分的技术措施。为了保证作物正常生长，获取高产稳产，必须供给作物以充足的水分。在自然条件下，往往因降水量不足或分布的不均匀，不能满足作物对水分要求。因此，必须人为地进行灌溉，以补天然降雨之不足。</common:generalComment>
